Here are the steps to run this repo:-
 - To clone this repo:- 
   - To Clone this Repo, Run this command: `git clone https://github.com/Rishabhpatidar91/Markdown.git`
   - Now run `nvm use` in both the frontend & backend folder before installing the packages.
   - Install the correct node version before installing the packages.
   - Now install the packages in both frontend and backend using the `npm install` command.
   - now run both the frontend and the backend using the `npm start` command.
   - Now you can test the application.

